    {
      "chinese": "採收季節到來，全村攜老扶幼，頭戴斗笠、手戴手套、腳穿雨鞋，帶著竹竿、畚箕、網子和麻袋，努力採收著紅肉李。天空飄著雨，每個人臉上滿是汗水，衣服濕透了，腳踩在濕滑的石頭上不斷摔跤，手上臉上被樹枝刮了好幾道傷痕，但豐碩的收成讓我們忘卻身體的疲累。",
      "ab": "rex na palamu’ ci napol, mara’aras ka nabkis lu ule’. bale’ maktaṟasi’, maktebukuro, makamegucu. rumili’ ci totah, pungki’, ami’, ṟubing, kunhapṟow lumamu’ ci anbari’. ana sunṟaṟobi’ ka kaṟal, mahuṟi’ na rinang ka hi’ lu lukus, icaki tahṟuti’ kunlakah ci uṟati’ matakuṟ. ma’ilis kora’ ka raṟes lu hi’ kinugus na araw anbari’. ga, ṟungen kora’ ka kinnawit na hi’ i payux ka linamu’.",
      "order": "2",
      "sound": "https://dzywvpqnys6mw.cloudfront.net/files/2020/11/26/8677065f187e98d8beacdc700e49f6ef.wav",
